<h1>What is a Pattern?</h1>

<p class=MsoNormal><i>Each pattern describes a problem which occurs over and
over again in our environment, and then describes the core of the solution to that
problem, in such a way that you can use this solution a million times over,
without ever doing it the same way twice<o:p></o:p></i></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:.5in'><b>C. Alexander</b>, “<i>The
Timeless Way of Building</i>”, 1979</p>

<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

